\c 2
\s Ruponeso inyasha dzaMwari
\p
\v 1 \add Wakakumutsai\add*, imwiwo makange makafa mukudarika nemuzvivi,
\v 2 zvamaifamba mazviri kare nemutowo wenyika ino, nenzira yemutungamiriri wesimba redenga, remweya unobata zvino muvana vekusateerera;
\v 3 nesu tose taifamba pakati pavo kare mukuchiva kwenyama yedu, tichiita kuda kwenyama nekwefungwa, nepachisikigo isu taiva vana vekutsamwirwa, sevamwewo.
\v 4 Asi Mwari, wakafuma panyasha, nekuda kwerudo rwake rukuru rwaakatida narwo,
\v 5 kunyange takange takafa mukudarika, wakatimutsa pamwe naKristu (makaponeswa nenyasha);
\v 6 uye aka\add ti\add*mutsa pamwe \add naye\add*, aka\add ti\add*garisa pamwe \add naye\add* ku\add nzvimbo \add*dzekumatenga muna Kristu Jesu;
\v 7 kuti munguva dzinouya aratidze fuma hurusa yenyasha dzake muunyoro kwatiri muna Kristu Jesu;
\v 8 nekuti nenyasha makaponeswa nerutendo, uye izvi hazvibvi kwamuri; chipo chaMwari;
\v 9 ha\add zvi\add*bvi pamabasa, kuti kusava neunozvikudza.
\v 10 Nekuti tiri basa rake, takasikirwa mabasa akanaka muna Kristu Jesu, Mwari aakagara agadzira, kuti tifambe maari.
\s VaJudha nevahedheni vakasanganiswa muna Kristu Jesu
\p
\v 11 Naizvozvo rangarirai kuti imwi maimbova vahedheni munyama, vanonzi kusadzingiswa nechinonzi kudzingiswa munyama kunoitwa nemaoko,
\v 12 kuti panguva iyo makange musina Kristu, muri vatorwa paubwo hwaIsraeri, uye vatorwa pasungano dzechivimbiso, musina tariro, uye musina Mwari munyika.
\v 13 Asi ikozvino muna Kristu Jesu, imwi maimbova kure, mava pedo neropa raKristu.
\v 14 Nekuti iye rugare rwedu, wakaita zviviri \add zvive\add* chimwe, uye wakaputsa mudhuri wepakati wekuparadzanisa,
\v 15 aparadza munyama yake ruvengo, \add iwo\add* mutemo wemirairo pazviga, kuti asike maari pavaviri munhu umwe mutsva, aite rugare,
\v 16 uye kuti ayananise vaviri kuna Mwari mumuviri umwe nemuchinjikwa, auraya ruvengo nawo,
\v 17 uye wakasvika akaparidza rugare kwamuri \add imwi\add* maiva kure, nekune vaiva pedo;
\v 18 nekuti nemaari tose tine mapindiro neMweya umwe kuna Baba.
\v 19 Naizvozvo zvino hamusisiri vaeni uye vatorwa, asi vebwo pamwe nevatsvene uye veimba yaMwari.
\v 20 Makavakwa pamusoro penheyo dzevaapositori nevaporofita, Jesu Kristu amene \add ari\add* \add ibwe\add* repakona.
\v 21 Maari chivakwa chose chakabatanidzwa chikure chive tembere tsvene muna Ishe,
\v 22 maari nemwiwo makavakwa pamwe muve ugaro hwaMwari muMweya.
